        {
            "title": "地平綫機器人盈轉虧因公允值變動  收入增近58%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">地平綫機器人(09660)公布，截至2025年1231日止，虧損104.69億元(人民幣‧下同)，去年同期盈利23.47億元，變幅546.2%。每股虧損81分，不派末期息。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"地平綫機器人官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/09660-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"地平綫機器人官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/09660-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">地平綫機器人官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">經調整虧損淨額28.12億元，按年升67.3% ; 經調整經營虧損23.72億元，按年升58.7%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">收入37.58億元，按年升57.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公布稱，2025年錄得優先股及其他金融負債的公允價值變動虧損66.64億元，而2024年則錄得收益46.77億元。於2025年的公允價值虧損包括(i)主要是可轉換借款的增量公允價值，與不斷增長的市值相符；及(ii)<br/>   D-Robotics發行的優先股的公允價值的增加。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2024年的公允價值收益則歸因於優先股負債公允價值的下調，該下調是由於首次公開發售時的實際轉換價格低於先前計量的該等優先股價值所致。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15765028-%e5%9c%b0%e5%b9%b3%e7%b6%ab%e6%a9%9f%e5%99%a8%e4%ba%ba%e7%9b%88%e8%bd%89%e8%99%a7%e5%9b%a0%e5%85%ac%e5%85%81%e5%80%bc%e8%ae%8a%e5%8b%95-%e6%94%b6%e5%85%a5%e5%a2%9e%e8%bf%9158",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508028_FI_source-web_09660-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-20 09:10:50",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期跌79點   ADR低水226點   阿里巴巴低水7.4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期報25357，跌79點或0.31%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">根據高盛網站，港股ADR較恒指昨日收市低水226點或0.89%，報25274點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">阿里巴巴(09988)第三季業績大遜預期， ADR較港收市價較港收市價低7.4%，報122.3元 ; 騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣507.83元，較香港收市價低1% ; 小米(01810) ADR收市折合港幣35.39元，較香港收市價低2.6% ; 美團 (03690)ADR收市折合港幣78.96元，較香港收市價低2.2%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報124.49元，較香港收市價高0.4% ; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣82.64元，較香港收市價低0.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">李寧(02331) ADR較香港收市價高2.7%，折合20.29港元 。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指夜市期指收報25312點，跌151點，較昨日恒指收市25500點，低水189點，成交32821張。國指夜市期指收報8637點，較昨日國指收市低水59點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15765017-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e8%b7%8c79%e9%bb%9e-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4226%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b47-4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-20 09:00:42",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "布油曾飆11%破119美元  紐約期油重越百關後倒跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">油價周二（19日）早段急升後顯著回落，全日走勢大幅波動。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"油價\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20200413-CH-oil_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"油價\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20200413-CH-oil_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">油價</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紐約期油4月合早段一度重上100美元大關，升逾5%至101.48美元，但其後由升轉跌，最終收報96.14美元，倒跌約0.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">倫敦布蘭特期油5月合約早段一度飆升近11%，高見每桶119.13美元，貼近上周初創下的逾3年半高位。其後升幅急速收窄，最終收報108.65美元，全日僅升約1.2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15764682-%e5%b8%83%e6%b2%b9%e6%9b%be%e9%a3%8611%e7%a0%b4119%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83-%e7%b4%90%e7%b4%84%e6%9c%9f%e6%b2%b9%e9%87%8d%e8%b6%8a%e7%99%be%e9%97%9c%e5%be%8c%e5%80%92%e8%b7%8c",
